00:27:14,710 --> 00:27:15,970
we made a plan

291
00:27:16,470 --> 00:27:18,290
to join a tour group to Mount Wu together.

292
00:27:23,600 --> 00:27:25,420
It wasn't just so the two of us could meet.

293
00:27:26,710 --> 00:27:27,770
[Pen Pal Match: Qian Yu]
It was also actually

294
00:27:27,790 --> 00:27:29,100
to set our parents up.

295
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:30,780
[Pen Pal Match: Nihai Pianxian]

296
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:32,180
If it worked out,

297
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:33,970
we could

298
00:27:33,990 --> 00:27:35,140
become a family

299
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:39,420
and become real sisters.

300
00:27:46,070 --> 00:27:46,660
Okay.

301
00:27:46,680 --> 00:27:48,140
Let's do a roll call.

302
00:27:48,470 --> 00:27:49,340
Wang Zusheng?

303
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:49,860
Here.

304
00:27:51,160 --> 00:27:52,340
Qiao Suqing?

305
00:27:52,710 --> 00:27:53,100
Here.

306
00:27:55,070 --> 00:27:55,940
Fang Xiuhong?

307
00:27:56,070 --> 00:27:56,530
Present.

308
00:27:57,310 --> 00:27:58,420
Xu Zhihong?

309
00:27:58,960 --> 00:27:59,420
Right here.

310
00:28:00,230 --> 00:28:01,100
Xu Meng?

311
00:28:01,790 --> 00:28:02,250
Here too.

312
00:28:06,470 --> 00:28:07,580
Everyone, stay close.

313
00:28:07,600 --> 00:28:08,380
Watch your step.

314
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:10,450
Everyone,

315
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:12,380
right beneath our feet

316
00:28:12,400 --> 00:28:13,180
is the famous

317
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,420
Mount Wu Slot.

318
00:28:14,840 --> 00:28:15,380
Now,

319
00:28:15,400 --> 00:28:17,620
remember when walking on the suspension bridge,

320
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,770
no running or jumping.

321
00:28:18,790 --> 00:28:19,490
Stay safe.

322
00:28:19,840 --> 00:28:21,180
Those in the back, please keep up.

323
00:28:30,270 --> 00:28:30,620
Here.

324
00:28:32,360 --> 00:28:33,100
Wear mine.

325
00:28:36,160 --> 00:28:37,180
Alright, everyone.

326
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,940
We're about to head up the mountain.

327
00:28:38,960 --> 00:28:40,330
Watch your step and stay safe.

328
00:28:50,510 --> 00:28:51,530
Everyone,

329
00:28:51,550 --> 00:28:53,210
we must be careful with our footing.

330
00:28:53,230 --> 00:28:54,770
The path is a bit slippery today.

331
00:28:58,960 --> 00:28:59,420
What's wrong?

332
00:29:00,230 --> 00:29:00,690
Are you okay?

333
00:29:00,710 --> 00:29:02,050
Why is the fog so thick?

334
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,010
I can't even see the road.

335
00:29:03,030 --> 00:29:03,730
Everyone,

336
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,380
don't panic.

337
00:29:04,840 --> 00:29:05,530
This kind of weather

338
00:29:05,550 --> 00:29:06,820
is very common on Mount Wu.

339
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:07,970
How about this?

340
00:29:08,310 --> 00:29:09,050
Let us

341
00:29:09,070 --> 00:29:09,860
all hold hands.

342
00:29:12,710 --> 00:29:13,340
Sister,

343
00:29:13,360 --> 00:29:13,830
don't be afraid.

344
00:29:14,440 --> 00:29:15,110
I'm right here with you.

345
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:20,820
Steady now.

346
00:29:22,030 --> 00:29:22,420
Mom...

347
00:29:23,600 --> 00:29:25,010
I'm having a hard time breathing.

348
00:29:25,710 --> 00:29:26,660
Come and rest here for a bit.

349
00:29:27,030 --> 00:29:27,490
Sit down.

350
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:31,960
Hey,

351
00:29:32,160 --> 00:29:33,820
we really can't stay here.

352
00:29:33,840 --> 00:29:34,490
Once it gets dark,

353
00:29:34,510 --> 00:29:35,660
it'll be freezing cold.

354
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:37,050
What's wrong with waiting a moment?

355
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,770
Can't you be a little considerate?

356
00:29:38,790 --> 00:29:39,380
If you want to die,

357
00:29:39,400 --> 00:29:40,580
don't drag us down with you.

358
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:41,250
Why do you care about her?

359
00:29:41,270 --> 00:29:42,450
Let's just get moving.

360
00:29:42,470 --> 00:29:43,820
Fine. You guys rest for a while,

361
00:29:43,840 --> 00:29:44,820
but catch up quickly.

362
00:29:44,840 --> 00:29:45,580
Hurry up.

363
00:29:47,600 --> 00:29:48,900
- I was unconscious then. - Qing!

364
00:29:50,070 --> 00:29:51,210
As for what happened later,

365
00:29:51,230 --> 00:29:52,490
I have no idea.

366
00:29:54,510 --> 00:29:55,580
When I woke up,

367
00:29:56,270 --> 00:29:57,730
Xu Meng and her father were gone.

368
00:29:59,400 --> 00:30:01,140
I was completely dazed.

369
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:02,970
I thought my mom

370
00:30:02,990 --> 00:30:04,580
had accidentally fallen off the cliff.

371
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:07,770
It felt like in the blink of an eye...

372
00:30:09,990 --> 00:30:10,730
Mom was gone.

373
00:30:12,680 --> 00:30:13,450
My home was gone.

374
00:30:16,310 --> 00:30:17,450
Everything was gone.

375
00:30:24,230 --> 00:30:25,660
When did you run into

376
00:30:26,160 --> 00:30:26,970
Xu Meng again?

377
00:30:28,030 --> 00:30:29,290
About half a year later.

378
00:30:31,270 --> 00:30:32,570
When I came to Weiyang back then,

379
00:30:35,270 --> 00:30:36,530
I stayed at Yao Baiyuan's place.

380
00:31:08,640 --> 00:31:09,660
That night,

381
00:31:10,880 --> 00:31:12,140
we talked a lot.

382
00:31:13,680 --> 00:31:14,490
That's when I learned

383
00:31:16,070 --> 00:31:17,490
that after returning from Mount Wu,

384
00:31:18,840 --> 00:31:19,690
her life

385
00:31:21,120 --> 00:31:22,660
wasn't much better than mine.

386
00:31:29,710 --> 00:31:30,210
Where's the medicine?

387
00:31:30,230 --> 00:31:30,620
Medicine!

388
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:32,420
Where did you hide the medicine?

389
00:31:35,470 --> 00:31:36,490
Where did you put the medicine?

390
00:31:38,260 --> 00:31:38,830
Medicine!

391
00:31:39,020 --> 00:31:39,550
Medicine!

392
00:31:40,310 --> 00:31:40,820
Where's the medicine?

393
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:43,210
It's all your fault

394
00:31:43,230 --> 00:31:45,010
that I've ended up like this!

395
00:31:45,400 --> 00:31:47,380
I need my medicine!

396
00:31:48,400 --> 00:31:48,940
You!

397
00:31:50,510 --> 00:31:52,100
- Dad, please stop hitting me!
- Get me my medicine!

398
00:31:52,120 --> 00:31:53,010
I was wrong, Dad!

399
00:31:53,640 --> 00:31:54,820
- Dad, please stop!
- I need my medicine!

400
00:31:54,840 --> 00:31:56,140
I was wrong, Dad!

401
00:31:57,940 --> 00:32:02,420
[Qihuang Clinic]

402
00:32:06,070 --> 00:32:06,940
Master Zhang,

403
00:32:08,270 --> 00:32:09,100
I'm here for the medicine.

404
00:32:09,120 --> 00:32:09,770
Master Zhang?

405
00:32:14,920 --> 00:32:15,730
Master Zhang.

406
00:32:36,550 --> 00:32:37,530
Back then,

407
00:32:38,960 --> 00:32:40,620
we were like two

408
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:43,340
elk caught in a snare.

409
00:32:43,840 --> 00:32:45,180
Neither of us could escape,

410
00:32:45,990 --> 00:32:47,210
and neither could help the other.

411
00:32:48,230 --> 00:32:48,940
All we could do

412
00:32:48,960 --> 00:32:50,580
was watch each other in silence.

413
00:32:52,750 --> 00:32:53,620
Six months later,

414
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:56,940
I managed to escape first.

415
00:33:09,510 --> 00:33:09,860
Sister.

416
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:19,210
A Chinese New Year's gift.

417
00:33:23,230 --> 00:33:24,380
Take a look.

418
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:27,450
It's beautiful.

419
00:33:29,790 --> 00:33:30,580
It must have been expensive.

420
00:33:31,270 --> 00:33:32,010
It didn't cost anything.

421
00:33:32,790 --> 00:33:33,620
Mr. Yao gave it to me.

422
00:33:38,790 --> 00:33:39,860
Happy Chinese New Year, Sister.

423
00:33:41,260 --> 00:33:42,820
[Double Fish]

424
00:33:55,030 --> 00:33:55,940
He hit you again?

425
00:33:58,880 --> 00:33:59,820
Do you like

426
00:34:00,790 --> 00:34:01,490
this gift?

427
00:34:09,670 --> 00:34:10,300
I do.

428
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:29,450
Happy Chinese New Year,

429
00:34:30,440 --> 00:34:30,970
Sister.

430
00:34:35,320 --> 00:34:36,130
Happy

431
00:34:36,150 --> 00:34:36,740
Chinese New Year.

432
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:39,260
Sister, what's wrong?

433
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,490
Yao is finally gone.

434
00:35:43,110 --> 00:35:43,530
Is there still

435
00:35:43,550 --> 00:35:44,740
something making you unhappy?

436
00:35:46,280 --> 00:35:46,900
I was thinking,

437
00:35:49,470 --> 00:35:50,490
what's going to happen to you?

438
00:35:52,280 --> 00:35:53,340
When will you be able

439
00:35:53,360 --> 00:35:54,650
to get away from the guy?

440
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:57,530
Meng,

441
00:35:58,190 --> 00:35:58,490
why don't you

442
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,610
move into my place?

443
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:05,560
Don't go back to that house anymore.

444
00:36:09,600 --> 00:36:10,880
He's my father.

445
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,300
I've owed him since the day I was born.

446
00:36:24,240 --> 00:36:25,090
I'm not as lucky

447
00:36:26,760 --> 00:36:27,610
as you.

448
00:36:29,960 --> 00:36:31,170
An "accident" like that

449
00:36:34,590 --> 00:36:36,130
doesn't happen that easily.

450
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:47,050
So you didn't know

451
00:36:48,150 --> 00:36:49,010
that Yao Baiyuan

452
00:36:49,630 --> 00:36:51,090
might have been killed by Xu Meng?

453
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:53,610
At the time, I really thought

454
00:36:53,630 --> 00:36:54,910
it was an accident.

455
00:36:55,990 --> 00:36:56,740
Then, how did

456
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,740
Xu Zhihong die?

457
00:37:00,920 --> 00:37:01,900
Xu Meng said

458
00:37:03,150 --> 00:37:04,260
it was all for me.

459
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:14,780
Dad,

460
00:37:15,070 --> 00:37:16,340
what are you doing?

461
00:37:16,840 --> 00:37:17,490
Close the door.

462
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:18,300
Hurry up!

463
00:37:18,630 --> 00:37:19,170
Close it!

464
00:37:23,240 --> 00:37:23,940
Leave Weiyang.

465
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,690
Pack your things

466
00:37:24,690 --> 00:37:25,610
right now.

467
00:37:25,630 --> 00:37:26,550
We're leaving now.

468
00:37:26,550 --> 00:37:27,320
But Dad,

469
00:37:27,800 --> 00:37:28,700
why do we have to

470
00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:29,780
leave Weiyang?

471
00:37:29,800 --> 00:37:30,260
You ask why?

472
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:31,820
I'll tell you why!

473
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:33,420
Behind my back,

474
00:37:33,880 --> 00:37:34,650
you took out

475
00:37:34,670 --> 00:37:35,820
so many shark loans.

476
00:37:36,550 --> 00:37:37,340
Those people are already

477
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:38,490
at our doorstep.

478
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:39,860
If we don't leave,

479
00:37:40,400 --> 00:37:42,010
we're just staying here to die?

480
00:37:43,190 --> 00:37:45,130
I'll find a way to pay them back.

481
00:37:46,070 --> 00:37:47,170
Can we please not leave?

482
00:37:47,550 --> 00:37:48,260
Pay them with what?

483
00:37:49,070 --> 00:37:50,090
By selling yourself?

484
00:37:50,510 --> 00:37:51,340
That's enough.

485
00:37:51,360 --> 00:37:52,570
Go pack your clothes!

486
00:37:52,760 --> 00:37:53,450
Move!

487
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:54,260
Go!

488
00:37:54,280 --> 00:37:55,490
Dad, don't force me.

489
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:56,570
You won't leave,

490
00:37:56,590 --> 00:37:57,700
and I'm "forcing" you?

491
00:37:57,960 --> 00:37:59,380
Is it because of the wretch?

492
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:02,620
You ungrateful brat!

493
00:38:03,670 --> 00:38:04,530
I'm the one

494
00:38:04,550 --> 00:38:05,740
who gave you life.

495
00:38:06,630 --> 00:38:07,090
Go.

496
00:38:08,070 --> 00:38:08,900
You're coming with me.

497
00:38:09,920 --> 00:38:11,220
Dad, don't touch that.

498
00:38:12,190 --> 00:38:12,820
Did the wretch

499
00:38:13,180 --> 00:38:14,340
give you this outfit?

500
00:38:15,400 --> 00:38:16,130
Dad, don't.

501
00:38:16,440 --> 00:38:17,700
Let go of me.

502
00:38:17,720 --> 00:38:18,410
Let go.

503
00:38:18,590 --> 00:38:19,430
Let go!

504
00:38:20,010 --> 00:38:21,120
You won't come with me?

505
00:38:21,470 --> 00:38:22,010
Are you coming?

506
00:38:22,030 --> 00:38:23,740
Dad, don't force me.

507
00:38:24,110 --> 00:38:25,050
I'm forcing you?

508
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:27,170
I'm forcing you?

509
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,090
You don't want to leave?

510
00:38:29,550 --> 00:38:30,260
That's fine.

511
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,050
I'll go find

512
00:38:31,070 --> 00:38:32,940
the wretch right now

513
00:38:32,960 --> 00:38:33,740
and beat her to death!

514
00:38:34,680 --> 00:38:35,930
Now, are you coming?

515
00:38:57,150 --> 00:38:58,340
The

516
00:38:58,360 --> 00:38:59,530
wretch...

517
00:38:59,550 --> 00:39:01,050
If it weren't for her

518
00:39:01,280 --> 00:39:01,860
back then,

519
00:39:02,550 --> 00:39:04,660
I wouldn't have

520
00:39:04,660 --> 00:39:06,930
ended up like this.

521
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:08,260
I'm going to

522
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,380
kill her.

523
00:39:09,840 --> 00:39:11,700
I'll kill her...

524
00:39:14,720 --> 00:39:15,170
Medicine...

525
00:39:15,670 --> 00:39:16,170
Medicine...

526
00:39:16,720 --> 00:39:17,700
Give it to me.

527
00:39:17,720 --> 00:39:18,220
Medicine...

528
00:39:20,590 --> 00:39:21,300
My medicine.

529
00:39:22,920 --> 00:39:23,380
Quick.

530
00:39:24,550 --> 00:39:25,160
Hurry...

531
00:39:25,370 --> 00:39:27,080
Get me my medicine.

532
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,170
What happened?

533
00:40:33,670 --> 00:40:34,170
Sister,

534
00:40:35,590 --> 00:40:37,050
when your mom fell off the cliff,

535
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:38,970
it wasn't an accident.

536
00:40:41,030 --> 00:40:42,340
He was the one who pushed her.

537
00:40:52,510 --> 00:40:53,010
Qing.

538
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:53,860
Qing.

539
00:40:54,150 --> 00:40:55,340
Qing, what's wrong?

540
00:40:55,360 --> 00:40:56,170
- Sister. - Qing.

541
00:40:56,190 --> 00:40:56,940
You fainted from the cold.

542
00:40:57,110 --> 00:40:57,450
Sister,

543
00:40:57,470 --> 00:40:59,340
- wake up.
- He tried to take your coat for warmth.

544
00:41:00,240 --> 00:41:00,860
Qing.

545
00:41:00,880 --> 00:41:01,430
Sister...

546
00:41:04,150 --> 00:41:05,090
What are you doing?

547
00:41:05,670 --> 00:41:06,860
She's not going to make it anyway.

548
00:41:07,110 --> 00:41:07,650
This coat should be

549
00:41:07,670 --> 00:41:09,260
given to someone who can survive.

550
00:41:09,370 --> 00:41:11,010
What are you talking about?

551
00:41:11,030 --> 00:41:12,530
- Stop it. - Let go.

552
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:13,570
Stop fighting.

553
00:41:13,590 --> 00:41:14,090
Stay out of this.

554
00:41:14,110 --> 00:41:15,340
Your mom tried to stop him,

555
00:41:15,920 --> 00:41:17,300
so he started wrestling with her.

556
00:41:18,440 --> 00:41:18,940
Dad.

557
00:41:19,720 --> 00:41:20,220
Dad.

558
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:23,490
Dad.

559
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:25,740
Dad.

560
00:41:26,960 --> 00:41:27,940
Dad...

561
00:41:28,440 --> 00:41:29,340
Help.

562
00:41:29,360 --> 00:41:30,940
Is anyone there?

563
00:41:30,960 --> 00:41:31,650
Help.

564
00:41:31,670 --> 00:41:32,570
Help.

565
00:41:32,590 --> 00:41:33,970
Is anyone there?

566
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:35,450
Help.

567
00:42:03,470 --> 00:42:04,530
He thinks his illness

568
00:42:04,550 --> 00:42:05,340
is all our fault.

569
00:42:06,400 --> 00:42:07,340
He tortures me every day,

570
00:42:08,110 --> 00:42:09,130
and now he wants to come after you.

571
00:42:10,400 --> 00:42:11,260
I had no other choice.

572
00:42:48,470 --> 00:42:49,220
Sister,

573
00:42:51,590 --> 00:42:52,740
from now on, we are

574
00:42:52,760 --> 00:42:53,610
real sisters.

575
00:42:56,110 --> 00:42:57,700
I will protect you with my life.

576
00:43:20,800 --> 00:43:21,490
Xu,

577
00:43:22,030 --> 00:43:22,940
inside your place,

578
00:43:22,960 --> 00:43:24,610
why is there all that banging?

579
00:43:25,240 --> 00:43:26,420
Is everything all right?

580
00:43:26,840 --> 00:43:29,050
My dad wanted to sell the large wardrobe.

581
00:43:29,360 --> 00:43:30,740
The door is too narrow,

582
00:43:30,760 --> 00:43:31,450
so we couldn't get it out.

583
00:43:32,990 --> 00:43:34,300
So I'm trying

584
00:43:34,320 --> 00:43:35,010
to chip at the door frame.

585
00:43:38,670 --> 00:43:39,420
By the way, Uncle Wang,

586
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:41,380
do you have...

587
00:43:42,440 --> 00:43:44,170
Oh, I've got mung bean soup on the stove.

588
00:43:44,190 --> 00:43:45,450
It's about to burn.

589
00:43:46,400 --> 00:43:47,130
It's burning.

